trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> 物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> object contains <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects that represent user profiles from a data source.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>物件包含<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo>代表從資料來源的使用者設定檔的物件。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>從傳回<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>，和<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> can be supplied to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete profile information and properties from the data source.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>可以提供給<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A>方法，以刪除資料來源的設定檔資訊和屬性。

trans-unit.source: The following code example allows a user to search for profiles using the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例可讓使用者設定檔使用的搜尋<xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>和<xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The user can pass the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> returned by the `find` methods to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete the associated profiles from the data source.
trans-unit.target: 使用者可以傳遞<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>傳回`find`方法<xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A>方法，以從資料來源中刪除相關聯的設定檔。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new, empty <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 建立新的空白 <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is constructed by profile provider implementers and returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>設定檔提供者實作器所建構，以及從傳回<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>，和<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>抽象類別。

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: 如需<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>實作會建立<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>資料存放區中的使用者設定檔，請參閱[實作設定檔提供者](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98)。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要加入至集合的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 將指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> 物件加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> method is commonly used by profile-provider implementers to populate a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> to return from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A>方法通常會使用設定檔提供者實作方式來擴展<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>從傳回<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>，或<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>抽象類別。

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: 如需<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>實作會建立<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>資料存放區中的使用者設定檔，請參閱[實作設定檔提供者](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98)。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the profile info collection is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出設定檔資訊集合是否具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Always <see langword="false" />, because thread-safe profile info collections are not supported.
trans-unit.target: 永遠為 <see langword="false" /> (因為不支援執行緒安全設定檔資訊集合)。

trans-unit.source: The collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 集合是唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: Makes the contents of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> read-only.
trans-unit.target: 使 <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> 的內容為唯讀。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method marks the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> as read-only so that <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects cannot be added to or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A>方法標記<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>以唯讀模式，讓<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo>物件無法加入或移除集合中。

trans-unit.source: After calling the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method, you cannot change the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> back to read/write.
trans-unit.target: 在呼叫<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A>方法，您無法變更<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection>回到讀取/寫入。

trans-unit.target: 因為不支援 <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> 物件的同步處理，故永遠為 <see langword="this" /> (在 Visual Basic 中為 <see langword="Me" />)。
